text:
e="preserve">Konstantina Kouteli (born 10 April 1981) is a Greek female water polo player.
She was part of the Greek women's national water polo team at the 2006 Women's European Water Polo Championship, 2006 FINA Women's Water Polo World Cup, and 2009 World Aquatics Championships.
